Clone a depository
    --> Create a depository on Github
    --> On Github click code and copy the url of the depository 
    --> On terminal --> git clone "the url of the depository"

Push
    --> Add --> we add the files in the selected directory
            --> git add + name of the files
            --> if we have more files --> git add file1 /file2 /file3 /

    --> Commit --> git commit

    --> Push --> to push into our remote repository all the files/changes done in local 
             --> git push